This paper discusses the use of 5G technology for universal Internet access, which falls under the category of networking and communication (cs.NI). The paper also discusses technical challenges and solutions related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), cybersecurity (cs.CYBER), and system engineering (cs.SY).
